# Lid-driven cavity flow at Re = 100
# Validation: Ghia et al. (1982)

Simulation cavity D2Q9
Domain  L = 1.0 x 1.0  N = 128 x 128
Physics nu = 0.128

Boundary north velocity(ux = 0.1, uy = 0)
Boundary south wall
Boundary east  wall
Boundary west  wall

Run 60000 steps
Output vtk every 10000 [rho, ux, uy]
